ent-AU14LACNHelmetStandard = LACN BK-9 Helmet
    .desc = Standard Issue Helmet used by LACN landing forces. Provides modest protection from bullets and melee attacks at the head.
ent-AU14LACNHelmetSL = LACN BK-9M Helmet
    .desc = A slightly more modern helmet made for LACN landing forces NCOs and Officers. This one contains a small built-in camera and has cushioning to protect your fragile brain.
ent-AU14LACNAirCrewHelmet = LACN LAH-99 aircrew helmet
    .desc = A helmet made for LACN aircrew. This one contains a small built-in camera and has cushioning to protect your fragile brain.
